mattools
-------------------------------------------------------------
This script was released under GPL license spring 2011 and is as such
free to use but without guarantees of support. See file COPYING for more
information on GPL.

The toolbox contains various handy functions when using Matlab, including
name-based figure-handling with connections to the LaTeX report base
"reportbase" found at https://github.com/jonatanolofsson/reportbase


Best regards,
Jonatan Olofsson
[jonatan.olofsson, gmail]
-------------------------------------------------------------

1) Installation
To install mattools, simply make sure the directory where you put it is
in Matlab's path
